  "whatsapp_greeting": "Hello / Hej / Inuiaqatigiissitassatut! I'm Sila's language assistant. I can help translate and bridge communication between local Greenlandic guides and international travelers. How can I help you today? / Hvad kan jeg hj\u00e6lpe dig med?",
